Wintersport fun in 9 close ski areas around Lake Millstätter See.

Snow dreams, beautiful ski runs and the sight to the silent white lake - winter sport around Lake Millstätter See makes winter wishes come true. The lake Millstätter See - The Jewel of Carinthia enchants one with its air of serenity and makes one feel like undertaking activities that are “off the beaten pistes”, like walking through the snow, to go sledding or ice-skating. To warm up you can visit one of our wonderful Christmas markets to get cookies, sausages, mulled wine…or you listen to Advent concerts. 
It doesn’t matter if you want to explore Goldeck, Bad Kleinkirchheim, Nassfeld, Katschberg or Heiligenblut-Großglockner, you can use them with only one ski pass.

